uez \n|TKO\n|1 (4), {{small|1:36}}\n|Dec 18, 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|MEX}} {{small|Billar El Perro Salado, Tijuana, Mexico}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|\n|-\n|1\n|{{yes2}}Win\n|1\u20130\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|MEX}} Gonzalo Lopez\n|TKO\n|1 (4), {{small|0:33}}\n|Dec 11, 2015\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"| {{flagicon|MEX}} {{small|Billar El Perro Salado, [[Tijuana]], Mexico}}\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://box.live/boxers/devin-haney/ Devin Haney] at Box Live Profile \n*[http://boxrec.com/en/boxer/741718 Devin Haney] at BoxRec\n*[https://www.tapology.com/fightcenter/fighters/206790-devin-haney-the-dream Devin Haney] at Tapology Profile\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=Regional boxing titles}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Ivan Redkach]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title={{nowrap|[[IBF]]-USBA}} [[lightweight]] champion\n|years=May 11, 2018 \u2013 September 2018<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=[[Teofimo Lopez]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-new}}\n{{s-ttl|title=IBF {{nowrap|North American}} lightweight champion\n|years=September 28, 2018 \u2013 December 2018<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=Hurricane Futa}}\n{{s-ttl|title=WBC International lightweight champion\n|years=January 11, 2019 \u2013 July 2019<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=Viktor Kotochigov}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Daud Yordan]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[WBO]] {{nowrap|Inter-Continental}} lightweight champion\n|years=January 11, 2019 \u2013 July 2019<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=Thomas Mattice}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Joe Cordina]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[World Boxing Association|WBA]] International lightweight champion\n|years=May 25, 2019 \u2013 August 2019<br>Vacated}}\n{{s-vac|next=[[James Tennyson]]}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-text|style=background:#C1D8FF; font-weight: bold;|text=World boxing titles}}\n{{s-break}}\n{{s-vac|last=[[Omar Figueroa Jr.]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of WBC world cha