0140208020524/http://briarcliffschools.org/schools/middle_school|archive-date=February 8, 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Enrollment\">{{cite web|title=Schools Building Enrollments|url=http://briarcliff.ss.syntaxcom.com/community/school_enrollment|publisher=Briarcliff Manor School District|accessdate=January 27, 2014|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140202123114/http://briarcliff.ss.syntaxcom.com/community/school_enrollment|archivedate=February 2, 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Blue Ribbon Schools\">{{cite news|title=List of Blue Ribbon Schools|url=http://www.ed.gov/programs/nclbbrs/list-2003.pdf|accessdate=February 27, 2014}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Greenhouse1\">{{cite news|title=BMS Greenhouse Club Raises Funds for Clean Water|url=http://pleasantville.patch.com/groups/briarcliff-manor-school-news/p/bms-greenhouse-club-raises-funds-for-clean-water|accessdate=January 25, 2014|newspaper=Pleasantville-Briarcliff Manor Patch|date=June 7, 2013}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Greenhouse2\">{{cite news|title=Briarcliff MS Greenhouse Club Gets Hands-On|url=http://pleasantville.patch.com/groups/going-green/p/briarcliff-ms-greenhouse-club-gets-handson|accessdate=January 25, 2014|newspaper=Pleasantville-Briarcliff Manor Patch|date=May 21, 2013}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Greenhouse3\">{{cite news|title=Briarcliff Middle School Students Share Their Green Thumbs with Inner City School|url=http://education.lohudblogs.com/2008/04/21/briarcliff-middle-school-students-share-their-green-thumbs-with-inner-city-school/|accessdate=January 25, 2014|newspaper=The Journal News|date=April 21, 2008|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140123132441/http://education.lohudblogs.com/2008/04/21/briarcliff-middle-school-students-share-their-green-thumbs-with-inner-city-school/|archive-date=2014-01-23|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n<ref name=\"Greenhouse4\">{{cite news|title=Being green in Briarcliff|url=http://northernwestchester.lohudblogs.com/2010/03/22/being-green-in-briarcliff/|accessda