ony Callea]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | Eddy Rioseco\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | Ted Ely\n|-\n! Doctor Dillamond\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[John Horton (actor)|John Horton]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[William Youmans]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Timothy Britten Parker]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | Steven Skybell\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Martin Ball]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | Timothy Britten Parker\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | Rodney Dobson\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | [[Tom Flynn (American actor)|Tom Flynn]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" | David DeVries\n\n|-\n|}\n\n''Notable Replacements''\n\n* '''Elphaba:''' [[Shoshana Bean]] (Broadway, 1NT), [[Caroline Bowman]] (Broadway), [[Lisa Brescia]] (Chicago), [[Jackie Burns]] (1NT, Broadway, 2NT), [[Kristy Cates]] (Chicago), [[Carmen Cusack]] (1NT), [[Louise Dearman]] (London), [[Jennifer DiNoia]] (Broadway, London, 1NT, 2NT), [[Marcie Dodd]] (Broadway, 2NT, San Francisco), [[Kerry Ellis]] (London, Broadway), [[Eden Espinosa]] (Broadway, Los Angeles, San Francisco), [[Ana Gasteyer]] (Chicago, Broadway), [[Mandy Gonzalez]] (Broadway), [[Pippa Grandison]] (Melbourne), [[Ashleigh Gray]] (London), [[Emma Hatton]] (London), [[Alexia Khadime]] (London), [[Caissie Levy]] (Los Angeles), [[Victoria Matlock]] (1NT), [[Lindsay Mendez]] (Broadway), [[Julia Murney]] (1NT, Broadway), [[Vicki Noon]] (2NT), [[Nicole Parker]] (Broadway, 1NT), [[Jemma Rix]] (various Australian productions), [[Dee Roscioli]] (Chicago, Broadway, 1NT), [[Rachel Tucker]] (London, Broadway), [[Willemijn Verkaik]] (Stuttgart, Oberhausen, Scheveningen, London, Broadway), [[Donna Vivino]] (1NT), [[Jessica Vosk]] (2NT, Broadway), [[Teal Wicks]] (Los Angeles, San Francisco, Broadway), [[Lindsay Pearce]] (Broadway)\n* '''Glinda:''' [[Annaleigh Ashford]], [[Jenni Barber]], [[Gina Beck]], [[Katie Rose Clarke]], [[Louise Dearman]], [[Sophie Evans (performer)|Sophie Evans]], [[Kate Fahrner]], [